name: product01
description: Use this mason’s hand tools set to plaster, build walls, remodeling, or laying brick. You’re ready for nearly any masonry job with this 5 piece set. The mason’s hand tools feature hardened steel blades to withstand heavy use and clear-lacquered handles for comfort.
